file_content.text: It's no use. You need an Extractor's ID card to operate that elevator.
Don't worry about the elevator. Tell me how to open this cell.
The Imperials only bring prisoners here, to receiving. It's the Extractors who take us below for interrogation.
I'm a Balmorran who should have kept his mouth shut.
Get out of here while you still can. The Extractors will be back any....
Not very chatty now, are you, old man?
Looks like we have a security breach. And some new prisoners.
Looks like we have a security breach. And a couple new prisoners.
